{"tid":1847880,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"就黎冇得再戴口罩，政府澄清儲備為1000萬個","createTime":"2020-01-28T08:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T12:28:53.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c27dc15640ecc50bc2f686adbf1c926a48a1658d","tid":1847880,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:50:31.000Z","msg":"對於有報道指政府大量生產口罩，並有存貨多達一億個，政府發言人今日(26日)指有關消息毫無事實根據，並澄清指，政府物流服務署儲存的手術用口罩是供應給各政府部門作日常及應變計劃之用，物流署去年每月平均向懲教署購買110萬個口罩，即懲教署每月產量，而每月的平均支貨量相若。<br />\n<br />\n為配合政府傳染病應變計劃，物流署需儲備1000萬個口罩，以支援有關決策局和部門的運作需要。因應最近新型冠狀病毒感染疫情，在過去一星期，相關部門已陸續從物流署庫存提取口罩供前線人員使用。物流署已加大採購，補充儲備數量，確保有足夠口罩供各政策局及部門使用。就口罩存貨的使用期方面，根據記錄，現時有關存貨的最早生產期為2019年1月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200126/bkn-20200126152528164-0126_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200126%2Fbkn-20200126152528164-0126_00822_001.html&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb3HDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=31936c36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200126/bkn-20200126152528164-0126_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8768537a14b5e39265201fa6a5beba5cdf9bf077","tid":1847880,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:50:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">匿埋喺屋企出唔到街？<br />\n唔夠口罩唔敢出去？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Twitter 戰線永遠需要你！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">入去 <a href=\"http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb3HDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=59996b16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a> 撳 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">/task2</span></span> 拎任務</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Retweet + Like + Reply</span></span><br />\nTask 2 好缺人，大家快啲去幫手！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，撳幾個掣都做唔到？<br 